        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Natural Sugar Labeling Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides that the nutrition facts label of any single ingredient sugar, honey, agave, or syrup (including maple syrup) that is packaged and offered for sale does not require an added sugars declaration.</p>]]></text>
